snippet.title: RICH & MIND-BLOWING
snippet.description:
Rich & Mind-Blowing is a channel of our Rich Journey,  its a platform of Entrepreneur Mindset
& Luxury Lifestyle enthusiants where people passionate about Tech Billionaire Lifestyle.

Wheter you want to learn about the Billionaire Lifestyle of famous celebrities, or about the Richest Tech Entrepreneur like Elon Musk Tesla & SpaceX CEO or TOP 10  Athletes and other mind blowing people on the Forbes list , how they spends their millions, what supercar they drive , House Tour in the most expensive Real Estates in the world, money topics like tsla & bitcoin, and even some of the most mind-blowing tech news and top 10 engineering discoveries - we've got you covered.

Come to enjoy our rich journey, share and discuss their own take on success, and you can expect at least 2 mind blowing video every week to fill your weekly dose of entertaining brain food.
